values: March 02, 2011: I've defriended some kids. Sorry. You either haven't updated in a million years (and you probably aren't coming back), you don't talk to me, or you don't respond to the comments I leave you - why did you even bother friending me in the first place then? I want friends who will actually, like, idk, speak to me. So if you just randomly friend me, you will not be accepted. Also: don't friend me because you like my fanmixes - just watch the community for that.

i still can't grasp the concept that i won't live forever this is my dusty and riddled collection of quotes. please do not comment
